schools.name: Zan Wesley Holmes Jr Middle School

data.description: Perfect starter home or for someone looking to downsize. This charming bungalow is perched high atop the street overlooking the greenbelt. Upon arrival you are greeted with a great covered front porch and large deck. Home includes fresh paint, granite counters, subway tile, ss appliances. Updated windows include plantation shutters. Refinished hardwoods. Roof, electrical service, plumbing, gas lines have been updated or replaced in the last 10 years. Backyard includes a storage shed. In the heart of the quickly growing Elmwood and moments from walking trails, Tyler Station, Bishop Arts, DART light rail, and Downtown. See attachments for additional information on recent city's plans for upcoming improvements and development in Elmwood. Buyer to verify schools and measurements.
